About.title: About me
About.description: I am a software developer with over two years of experience, specializing in front-end development with Next.js, React, and Redux. Graduated as a Full Stack Developer, I enjoy creating modern and efficient solutions. I recently moved to Switzerland, where I am continuing to develop my skills while adapting to a new environment.
